    "title": "Bringing AI Code Security into Qualys ETM",
    "description": "A first-class data model for the next generation of findings AI-driven code security is becoming a real category. Anthropic&#8217;s Claude Code Security and OpenAI&#8217;s Codex Security are the leading examples, and more will follow. These tools reason about source code at a depth that traditional SAST cannot reach, surfacing logic flaws, broken authentication patterns, hardcoded [&#8230;]",
